text: THIS APP IS AMAZING!!!!!!!!!! Don't get me wrong, it's not like it's a complex app that can entertain you for hours or anything, but it's a 5 star. It's really satisfying popping the bubbles, the sound is on point, and you can add vibration. There are hardly any adds, so you have that out of your way. It also IS stress releivant. Not calming, relieving. I 100 percent suggest getting thus app.

title: For all the people saying...
text: For all the people saying... "All it does is pop bubble wrap, don't waist your time!" It's supposed to be all you do, for some people it's pointless but if you are a figity person then this is perfect, so stop complaining. This does help some people. And also to the developers, it wouldn't hurt to make the bubbles smaller so you can pop more.

Amazing for lovers of bubble wraps. Effects makes it feel real: vibration,popping sounds & the way the bubble looks after & before being popped.   It has two modes:   1. Infinite mode: where the bubbles get refilled wz air after popping them to keep popping them continuously.  2. Normal mode: popped bubbles aren't filled wz air again & ur screen acts as a bubble wrap that you pop & finish.  It's a very good tool for releasing stress too.

My only complaint is the occasional bubble doesn't make a sound.  Just like real bubble wrap.  Ha ha. So is that really a complaint?  Straight forward and simple.  Best of these apps so far, no nuisances.
